Title: Calculating the volume of a glass of wine
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ivan Kostine
Maintainer: ivan.kostine@unil.ch
Description: This package contains the following function:
    - Building the function of a glass of wine
    - Benchmarking the different approaches
    - Calculating the integral of the function
    - Calculating the volume
    - Simulating a party
    - Finding the optimal volume needed to fill the glass 
    - Calculating the amount of bottles needed for a party
